game.name: Summer lake 15
game.description:
Wow! It is time to have some relaxing hours and enjoy fishing on the corner of a beautiful lake forest! We are pretty sure that you would not like to miss this opportunity especially when you find out a brand new fishing challenge on our website. Hey gamers! Grab your rod and get ready to collect as many fishes as you can to set your own huge score! There are different types of fishes including Velifer, Snakehead, Buffalo, Gar, Northern pike, Sunfish, Redhorse, Crucian, Bowfin and Bluegill to catch.

The best part is that you will be rewarded with a sufficient amount of money for every caught fish. Use that money to purchase new fishing locations, rods and bait to make your gameplay more interesting and challenging! You would have 7 types of fishing rods, 24 baits and 6 unique places to explore in this HTML5 fishing game. Most of fish species covered here are from North America and Europe. The wider range of lure and bait selections will help to keep you glued to the screen for long.

Put your finger on your mouse to cast, reel and choose the on-screen items and make sure that you catch as many fishes as you can to secure the top position on the leaderboard! Summer Lake is a cool online game where you are allowed to discover amazing fishing areas. Keep your eyes on both small and big fishes and make sure to get all the improvements including lures, rods, and new places! Throw bait by targeting the place and get ready to catch some high-valued fishes fast! Good luck to play some more popular titles from the category of free arcade games that are playable on multiple devices, no download required!
